#

Lemon-Glazed Pork Parmesan with Spicy Tomato Ragu

$18.99
550 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

PorkItalianComfort Food

Description

A delightful dish combining succulent pork with a zesty lemon glaze, complemented by a rich and spicy tomato sauce.

Ingredients

  • Pork chops: 4 pieces
  • Parmesan cheese: 1 cup, grated
  • Lemon juice: 1/4 cup
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic cloves: 4, minced
  • Tomato sauce: 2 cups
  • Red pepper flakes: 1 teaspoon
  • Oregano: 1 teaspoon
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Fresh parsley: for garnish
  • Lemon zest: 1 tablespoon
